{"tid":883303,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企兩老好撚迷信！！！有冇巴絲有相同處景","createTime":"2018-10-30T17:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T19:37:42.000Z","uid":79171,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e987651046d81976e82175a221203029439007d2","tid":883303,"uid":79171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"交待少少背景先......<br />\n細佬我屋企人係做生意的 所以就相當迷信<br />\n做咩都要問過d相士/風水佬<br />\n又話我腳頭好, 一出世屋企就開始發圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算係有兩個臭錢 (認真唔係曬命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n細佬我畢咗業一年多D<br />\n有一個拍咗拖六年的女朋友, <br />\n佢屋企就普通受薪階層啦 有兩個細妹 有一層自住私樓(舊區舊樓) <br />\n可以話女朋友比咗大部份的青春我(高中到大學再到畢業,而家24)<br />\n大家都係第一次拍拖 都係食咗對方隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁都見曬家長, 本來都相安無事 一開頭我老豆老母都無嫌人窮 <br />\n都幾出乎我意料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但就最近一個月前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我阿媽同我地兩個食飯時<br />\n我阿媽無啦啦就睇到我女朋友隻手係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">斷掌</span></strong><br />\n我老母即刻面都黑埋, 不過都冇即場爆發<br />\n返到去即刻對我女朋友的態度唔同曬<br />\n威脅我一定要同我女友分手, 一開頭都睬佢都有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我老豆出差返嚟知道之後都反應非常大<br />\n同我老母一樣都係要我即刻分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我同佢地都分別嘈咗幾次 話斷掌會勊夫勀子乜乜柒柒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直到前幾晚, 又一次嘈緊的時候我老豆突然之間跪咗係面前<br />\n好認真 好慘咁樣話: &quot;老豆我就得你呢一粒仔, 由細到大我都比你做自己鍾意的野, <br />\n從來都冇逼你做任何你唔想做的野, 但只有今次你一定要聽老豆講, 老豆真係唔想白頭人送黑頭人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &quot;<br />\n我由細到大都好尊敬我老豆, 佢識好多野,教我好多道理 係一個好老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢跪係到嗰一刻我都即刻跪返低扶返佢起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係我女朋友跟咗我好耐 雖然有少少脾氣 但總體嚟講都係一個好好的女仔<br />\n成六年感情 我真係真係唔想放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n而家真係左右做人難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打打就咁長 如果你睇到呢到 真係好多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望各位巴絲可以放低你的睇法, 有相同處景最好可以講下你地點拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n萬分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b82b654b5245bb5b2aa5d73886735e2e87b0c1","tid":883303,"uid":11336,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:37:00.000Z","msg":"求其搵個師傅問點化解 做吓樣比佢哋睇"},{"pid":"a4c10e47c2cfffa3995f7b374eea735fb7c97a65","tid":883303,"uid":118647,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"父母得一對，女朋友可以再搵過"},{"pid":"0088750a0505aa859a1fee753799b5fdc9187452","tid":883303,"uid":92,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:42:01.000Z","msg":"紋返條線上去"},{"pid":"61de22c82dce6d5c1a3a7dd9183a55901dfd5532","tid":883303,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:43:50.000Z","msg":"斷掌有咩問題"},{"pid":"2de086d7563e169ef5286bcc4f6057167289e44c","tid":883303,"uid":45431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:44:46.000Z","msg":"寧教人打仔 莫教人分妻<br />\n你老豆老母真係痴鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac763d49569ee090ce9f2ca2c25b6868f73ad00","tid"